caption.p: Effects of F-EO, L-EO, and S-EO on the LPS-induced RAW264.7 cell morphology (128 μg/mL) (a), NO production (b), and secretion of IL-6 (c) and TNF- α (d). The results of at least three independent experiments were expressed as mean ± SD values. (b-d) Different letters above bars represent a significant difference ( p < 0.05).
